How To Run
1) prepare_headers.sh
2) run_hmmscan.sh
3) run_diamond.sh
4) run_bbhsort.sh on each marker manually!

For #4 i did:

  ./run_bbhsort.sh ncbi_dataset/ parB > parBc.diamond.faa
  ./run_bbhsort.sh ncbi_dataset/ parA_AAA_31 > parA_AAA_31.diamond.faa

Then:


Directories tree:

markers
.
.
. . . marker1
      .
      .
      . . . hmmpressed files, Pfam files. See example for more information


ncbi_dataset
.
.
. . .data
     .
     .
     . . . <any_id_of_choice>
           .
           .
           . . .<any_filename>[.faa] #.faa extension required
